-- Vestas Chief Wants Meetings With G20 State Heads on Green Jobs
-- B y   C h r i s t i a n   W i e n b e r g
-- 2010-11-09T08:08:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/vestas-chief-wants-meetings-with-g20-state-heads-on-green-jobs.html
Ditlev Engel, chief executive officer
of Vestas Wind Systems A/S and convener of the working group for
creating green jobs, said he will ask every leader of the G20
countries for a one-hour meeting in the coming months to talk
about forming jobs for the renewable energy industry.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
